      • is

        public boolean is(java.lang.CharSequence other,
                  TextParameter.IsErrorCallback... errorCallbacks)
        Checks that the internal value of the TextParameter equals the provided CharSequence.

        The TextParameter.IsErrorCallback.isError(TextParameter, CharSequence) method on all the provided TextParameter.IsErrorCallback instances will be called if the check fails. The TextParameterErrorHandler.isError(TextParameter, CharSequence) methods on the instances of TextParameterErrorHandler provided to this object will not be called.

        Parameters:
        other - The CharSequence to compare the internal value of the TextParameter to.
        errorCallbacks - The TextParameter.IsErrorCallbacks called in case the check fails.
        Returns:
        true if the value equals the provided {code CharSequence}, false in all other cases.
